OL,3,CApple apologises after latest iPad
OL,4,Cadvert sparks backlash
OL,6,FIn a statement shared with Ad Age,
OL,7,FApple apologised for the video, and
OL,8,Fhas reportedly pulled it from
OL,9,Fappearing on television.
OL,11,FTor Myhren, the company's vice
OL,12,Fpresident of marketing communications,
OL,13,Fsaid in a statement provided to ITV
OL,14,FNews: "Creativity is in our DNA at
OL,15,FApple, and it's incredibly important
OL,16,Fto us to design products that empower
OL,17,Fcreatives all over the world.
