OL,6,F"Our goal is to always celebrate the
OL,7,Fmyriad of ways users express
OL,8,Fthemselves and bring their ideas to
OL,9,Flife through iPad. We missed the mark
OL,10,Fwith this video, and we're sorry."
OL,12,FThe new iPad has a thinner design,
OL,13,Fadded processing power, slightly
OL,14,Fupgraded storage and dual OLED panels
OL,15,Ffor a brighter display.
OL,17,FAmericus Reed II, professor of
OL,18,Fmarketing at The Wharton School of the
OL,19,FUniversity of Pennsylvania said he was
OL,20,F'disturbed' by the advert.
