OL,6,FHe said: "I understood conceptually
OL,7,Fwhat they were trying to do, but I
OL,8,Fthink the way it came across is, here
OL,9,Fis technology crushing the life of
OL,10,Fthat nostalgic sort of joy."
OL,12,FApple saw a drop of 17 percent in iPad
OL,13,Fsales last year during the January-
OL,14,FMarch period. The device currently
OL,15,Faccounts for around six percent of the
OL,16,Fcompany's sales.
